original: Öijer, Oscar Vilhelm, tandläkare, Linköping, f. 29/3/10 i Törnevalla, Ös-tergötl. 1., av O. L. Öijer o. Hilma Carolina Pettersson. G. 37 m. Elsa El-vine Östholm. Barn: Göran f. 39, Christina 41. — Stud:ex. i Linköp. 29, tandl :kand. 32, tandläk. 35. Assist, i Sthlm 35-36, däreft. praktik i Reftele, skoltandl. i Reftele o. Västboås, praktik i Linköp. sed. 42.
translated: Öijer, Oscar Vilhelm, dentist, Linköping, b. 29/3/10 in Törnevalla, Östergötland, Sweden, son of O. L. Öijer and Hilma Carolina Pettersson. Married in 1937 to Elsa Elvine Östholm. Children: Göran b. 1939, Christina b. 1941. Completed high school in Linköping in 1929, dental studies in 1932, became a dentist in 1935. Worked as an assistant in Stockholm from 1935 to 1936, followed by practice in Reftele and school dentistry in Reftele and Västboås. Started practice in Linköping in 1942.
